snippet.title: WARRIORS: Abyss - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Visit the official website: https://bit.ly/3QbNz3B

Descend into the Inferno.

WARRIORS: Abyss is now available on PlayStation®5, PlayStation®4, Xbox Series X|S, and Windows PC via Steam®. WARRIORS: Abyss will also be available on Nintendo Switch™ on February 14th, 2025.

Take command of historic and masterful warriors by challenging countless swarms of enemies. Through victory and defeat, traverse the merciless trials of hell.

Join the #KTFamily:
X: https://twitter.com/KoeiTecmoUS
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/koeitecmous
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/koeitecmous/
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/KTFamily
*Screens are taken from an in-development version.
